03c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e Obsidian comes with a dedicated theme store to change the entire app\u0026#39;s look, fonts, accent color, and iconography with just a single click. I used the Things theme (based on a popular task management app on Mac called Things 3) to give my Obsidian vault a neat makeover.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"5086-4ca2-838df1dec914\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.xda-developers.com/bear-is-the-best-note-taking-app-and-its-not-even-close/\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/reasons-why-bear-is-the-best-notes-app.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/reasons-why-bear-is-the-best-notes-app.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/reasons-why-bear-is-the-best-notes-app.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/reasons-why-bear-is-the-best-notes-app.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/reasons-why-bear-is-the-best-notes-app.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/reasons-why-bear-is-the-best-notes-app.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.xdaimages.co